tags.name: Vanha kirkko
tags.wheelchair:description: Pääovella portaat. Ota yhteys henkilökuntaan käyttääksesi sivuovea ja hissiä. Main door with steps. You need to contact the staff to get in with the elevator.

tags.name: Aleksanterin teatteri
tags.wheelchair:description: Wheelchair entrance and parking place are on the back: call the ticket office to ask someone to open the back door or have an assistant to do it. There are 4 wheelchair accessible spaces on the sides, 2 of which are small & hard to access.
